      <decision factor="Stockout Projection (Pillar 3)" rationale="Consumption velocity banner showing 'Days until ROP' per article. SVG sparklines for management. Proactive alerts before stockout occurs." source="Claude Roadmap + Gemini Hub (6)" />
      <decision factor="Fuzzy Search / Offline AI (Pillar 4)" rationale="Levenshtein distance + Soundex FR for duplicate article prevention. Prevents typo variants (e.g., 'Rame A4' vs 'Rame papier A4') without cloud API." source="Claude Roadmap + Gemini Hub (6)" />
